# Trading Safety

- Daily loss cap server-side; breach halts new entries and alerts.
- Per-market and per-account exposure caps.
- No orders without: heartbeat, websocket, auth, fresh price feed.
- Kill switch stops new entries within 1s and reconciles open positions.
- Live changes gated behind safe-live verification run.
- Never log secrets. Never commit .env. Never expose account IDs publicly.
